title: Backing Rahul Yadav’s 4B Networks was a mistake, says Info Edge’s Sanjeev Bikhchandani
description: The consumer internet group has initiated arbitration proceedings against its portfolio company 4B Networks, founded by Housing.com cofounder Rahul Yadav, after the startup failed to provide crucial information about its operations and management for a forensic audit.

title: Trade setup for Monday: Top 15 things to know before the opening bell
description: A short build-up was seen in 66 stocks, including Apollo Tyres, Max Financial Services, Britannia Industries, Info Edge India, and Laurus Labs. An increase in OI along with a fall in price points to a build-up of short positions.

title: Info Edge shares drop 2.41% as Sensex falls
description: The stock quoted a 52-week high of Rs 4984.1 and a 52-week low of Rs 3310.0.

title: Naukri parent Info Edge to invest Rs 10 crore in SaaS subsidiary Zwayam
description: Naukri.com parent Info Edge (India) Ltd on Friday said it will invest Rs 10 crore in its wholly-owned subsidiary Zwayam Digital Pvt Ltd. The investment is being done to meet the working capital requirement of Zwayam, Info Edge said in a statement.

title: Neutral Info Edge; target of Rs 4200: Motilal Oswal
description: Motilal Oswal recommended Neutral rating on Info Edge with a target price of Rs 4200 in its research report dated August 12, 2023.

title: Buy Info Edge (India); target of Rs 4896: Geojit
description: Geojit is bullish on Info Edge (India) has recommended buy rating on the stock with a target price of Rs 4896 in its research report dated August 24, 2023.
